    "Interesting future directions include: i) expanding AUTOACT to more realistic task scenarios (Puig et al., 2018; Zhou et al., 2023a; Xie et al., 2024), ii) boosting more knowledge via self-instruct (as analyzed in §5), iii) iteratively enhancing synthetic trajectories via self-improvement (Huang et al., 2023; Aksitov et al., 2023).",
